reviewText: I ORDERED THIS SET BUT WAS UNSATISFIED BECAUSE 1 DVD WAS MISSING.  JUST TOO MUCH TROUBLE TO RETURN THEM SO JUST KEPT IT. I WILL NEVER ORDER DVDS UNLESS NEW. MOVIE QUALITY NOT GOOD BECAUSE MOVIES SOUND IT VERY LOW.

Overall this isn't a good pack. Most of these movies are just horrible. There are maybe 5 that I was able to watch
till the end.
Granted, they are laughable. Way too much nudity that's not needed whatsoever.
If you like watching LOW budget films then this is will suit your needs well.
